verbose_text: We used two independent MOs designed to inhibit translation of XtEMSY (XtEMSY MO1 and XtEMSY MO2), and as controls we made use of the GeneTools control MO as well as MOs carrying five base mismatches compared with their specific versions (XtEMSY mMO1 and XtEMSY mMO2).
evidence: MOs designed to inhibit translation of XtEMSY
